---
title: Steak & Lemon-Parmesan Corn on the Cob with Sweet Balsamic Salad
description: Transform your next weeknight meal with this impressive, ultra-summery feast. You’ll start by searing savory bavette steaks and cooking corn on the cob. Then, you’ll slather the sweet corn with a creamy, tangy lemon-Parmesan sauce and pair it all with a fresh balsamic salad that features baby lettuce, tomatoes, and cucumber.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/686be95f5ba155634794fc40-498042af.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/686be95f5ba155634794fc40-en-US.pdf
servings: 2
